{"tid":828683,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tap＆Go手機錢包餘額突變負數　HKT認系統出問題 (21:30)","createTime":"2018-09-20T00:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T13:13:57.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19696393607e5a638e3ed38152a90541639b8c9f","tid":828683,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180919/img/20180919213020lc_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20180919%2Fimg%2F20180919213020lc_p1.jpg&h=b0987340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有用戶在Tap&amp;Go的fb專頁反映問題。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f1ac0eef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港電訊(HKT)旗下的Tap&amp;Go「拍住賞」手機付款程式系統今日(19日)一度出錯，多名用戶指其手機錢包餘額「正數變負數」，有人更指餘額突然變成「負2000元」。香港電訊證實，部分Tap&amp;Go「拍住賞」客戶的手機錢包餘額及交易紀錄，今日曾短暫出現問題，但下午已恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n在「Tap&amp;Go by HKT拍住賞」的Facebook專頁，今有多名用戶留言，指其儲值金額消失不見，甚至變成負數，有人稱「無啦啦啲錢無曬(晒)」、「我無咗千幾蚊」，亦有人指餘額本應約有500港元，「但變左(咗)負1千多d(啲)」；「我都係，無哂(晒)錢，仲要負2000，咩事呀」。<br />\n<br />\n香港電訊回覆東網查詢時指，部分客戶手機錢包餘額及交易紀錄今日曾短暫出現問題，但較早時已恢復正常，強調系統的安全性一直完好，客戶的手機錢包在今次事件中都安全。<br />\n<br />\n金融管理局發言人指，拍住賞手機錢包營運商已就事件通知金管局，該局已與營運商作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180919/20180919213020lc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20180919%2F20180919213020lc.html&d=9HFwKgiXanrvJ1lsAHvQR54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b468a2e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20180919/20180919213020lc.html</a>"},{"pid":"21c83b5ee4c71e5ff33b85c6c79d5488eeff185a","tid":828683,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:57:05.000Z","msg":"每人賠一百啦"},{"pid":"fe8c8a5e994e437c5f59494255bd5957e681fb9d","tid":828683,"uid":34174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"打手文又黎 駛唔駛又del tap&amp;go 呀今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631072f64706cf22fbe86c586d32b50f6d6c628c","tid":828683,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"跟本係夾埋谷金管局個新System<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06432ed91c5129ca64c80fce95420e4e781f9d7e","tid":828683,"uid":48759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:21:50.000Z","msg":"今日又係咁 無啦啦負一千"},{"pid":"571a07ffc1fd9ff77f30278b5c05ae47620ec187","tid":828683,"uid":175383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}